    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="site-wrapper">
            <div class="site-wrapper-inner">
                <div class="cover-container">
                    <div class="masthead clearfix">
                        <div class="inner">
                            <h3 class="masthead-brand">Chocolatey Explorer</h3>
                            <ul class="nav masthead-nav">
                                <li><a data-scroll-to="#features">Features</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="inner cover">
                        <h1 class="cover-heading">Chocolatey Explorer</h1>
                        <p class="lead">
                            Chocolatey Explorer is an application to make <a href="http://chocolatey.org" target="_blank">Chocolatey</a> that little bit more awesome
                            by giving you control over it's basic functions without having to break out PowerShell.
                        </p>
                        <p class="lead">
                            <a href="ChocolateyExplorer.application" class="btn btn-lg btn-default">Download Direct</a>
                        </p>
                        <p class="lead">
                            Or download with <a href="http://chocolatey.org/packages/ChocolateyExplorer" target="_blank">Chocolatey</a>
                            <pre>C:\ choco install ChocolateyExplorer</pre>
                        </p>
                        <p class="lead">
                            <a href="https://github.com/james-dibble/ChocolateyExplorer" target="_blank">Fork Chocolatey Explorer on GitHub.</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="container-fluid">
                        <div class="row" id="features">
                            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                                <div class="page-header">
                                    <h2>Features</h2>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                                <div class="panel panel-primary">
                                    <div class="panel-heading">Install</div>
                                    <div class="panel-body">
                                        Install your favorite packages with an exact version, even prerelease one.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                                <div class="panel panel-primary">
                                    <div class="panel-heading">Update or Uninstall</div>
                                    <div class="panel-body">
                                        View the packages you currently have installed and update or remove them.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                                <div class="panel panel-primary">
                                    <div class="panel-heading">Sources</div>
                                    <div class="panel-body">
                                        Add a custom Chocolatey source that is exposed via OData including Nuget based feeds.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                                <div class="panel panel-primary">
                                    <div class="panel-heading">Search</div>
                                    <div class="panel-body">
                                        Search for a particular package to install from a particular source or list all available packages.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
